author: sarowe
msg: SOLR-3344: Maven configuration: Add Jetty dependencies to the Solr test-framework POM template, so that those dependencies are transitively included when the Solr test-framework is used externally; remove the Jetty dependencies from the dataimporthandler and clustering Solr contribs' POM templates.  The optional Jetty dependencies in the solr-core module's POM template are left as-is, to facilitate JettySolrRunner's use as a cmdline utility.
